To build this project you will need to build openni:

The following is a good guide:
http://www.keyboardmods.com/2010/12/howto-kinect-openninite-skeleton.html

To build brokap in ubuntu:

    sudo apt-get install virtualenvwrapper
    mkdir ~/.virtualenvs
    mkvirtualenv brokap
    git clone https://nonameentername@github.com/nonameentername/brokap.git
    cd brokap
    pip install -r requirements.txt
    make

update brokap_blender.py to point to the source directory and open from blender.
